106
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,600
What are you thinking, Li Chang Ge?

107
00:07:36,839 --> 00:07:38,160
It's the Ashina Tribe you're talking about.

108
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:40,160
If you help Wang Jun Kuo because of this,

109
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,800
you'll be the greatest sinner of the Tang Dynasty.

110
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,000
Come in.

111
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:57,120
Your Highness.

112
00:07:57,839 --> 00:07:59,439
Are we departing today?

113
00:07:59,439 --> 00:08:00,439
Yes.

114
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:02,839
Wei Shu Yu's work is almost done.

115
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:04,600
We are meeting up with him today.

116
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:08,120
I'll take you to the east gate of the city later...

117
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:09,240
to meet Wei Shu Yu.

118
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,120
Are you not leaving?

119
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:12,360
