125
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:41,600
Please hurry and pack your things, Your Highness.

126
00:08:55,559 --> 00:08:57,210
Why are you locked up here too?

127
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:01,600
I know.

128
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,480
You're still mad at me.

129
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,519
Why are you in Youzhou?

130
00:09:08,159 --> 00:09:09,919
Was sending me off a cliff not enough?

131
00:09:11,679 --> 00:09:14,039
You won't give it a rest until you personally see me die.

132
00:09:14,039 --> 00:09:15,039
Chang Ge.

133
00:09:15,399 --> 00:09:16,399
I...

134
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:20,720
Stop talking.

135
00:09:21,639 --> 00:09:22,679
Get some rest.

136
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,960
Whether you believe me or not,

137
00:09:26,639 --> 00:09:29,000
I never betrayed you.

138
00:09:30,159 --> 00:09:32,240
Hao Du set me up that day...

139
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:33,840
to mess with your emotions.

140
00:09:34,210 --> 00:09:35,759
