141
00:09:37,559 --> 00:09:39,450
You still chose to succumb to him.

142
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:41,799
I'm sorry.

143
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:43,960
I don't want you...

144
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:45,639
to be locked up in prison because of me.

145
00:09:48,159 --> 00:09:49,159
You're thinking too much.

146
00:09:51,039 --> 00:09:53,159
I'm here because I tried to get blood from a stone...

147
00:09:54,210 --> 00:09:55,450
but hurt myself instead.

148
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,279
