151
00:10:00,879 --> 00:10:01,960
to Yan Li Khan.

152
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:04,450
That jerk is too ambitious.

153
00:10:04,919 --> 00:10:06,360
He's a traitor.

154
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:08,480
Is Prince of Lujiang not going to do anything about this?

155
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:10,450
Prince of Lujiang is the mastermind.

156
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,000
What?

157
00:10:12,399 --> 00:10:13,519
What are you going to do?

158
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,090
What should I do?

159
00:10:17,759 --> 00:10:19,039
Isn't this the ending...

160
00:10:20,210 --> 00:10:22,360
you and your new master want to see?

161
00:10:24,450 --> 00:10:25,450
Chang Ge.

162
00:10:26,210 --> 00:10:27,799
His Highness has always doted on you.

163
00:10:27,799 --> 00:10:29,000
- He never thought of...
- Stop it.

164
00:10:29,559 --> 00:10:31,519
Even if I shatter to pieces,

165
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:34,159
I won't succumb to Li Shi Min as you did.

166
00:10:43,240 --> 00:10:44,600
Did you come to Youzhou alone?

167
00:10:45,039 --> 00:10:46,039
No.

168
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:49,279
Hao Du and I are to meet at the city's east gate...

169
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:50,960
at 3:45pm today.

170
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,159
But trust me.

171
00:10:54,159 --> 00:10:55,799
I won't tell him I saw you.

172
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:57,960
Do you think you'll still get out alive to see Hao Du?

173
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,799
If you want to make it out alive,

174
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:04,080
you'll need his help.

175
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:10,600
Guards! I want to see Li Yuan!

176
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:12,399
- Guards!
- Chang Ge, what are you doing?

177
00:11:12,679 --> 00:11:13,679
