210
00:12:47,159 --> 00:12:48,679
- We can go now.
- All right.

211
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:50,799
I look forward to hearing good news from you.

212
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:52,120
Uncle Li Yuan.

213
00:12:52,559 --> 00:12:54,039
Wei Shu Yu is one of my people.

214
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:56,320
Even if he dies, he has to die by my hand.

215
00:12:56,960 --> 00:12:58,960
If anything happens to him,

216
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:01,000
I won't hold back.

217
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:25,879
Please.

218
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:42,279
Princess Yongning managed to safely escape from Chang'an.

219
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:45,360
Someone like that wouldn't fall into the hands of Wang Jun Kuo.

220
00:14:00,360 --> 00:14:02,519
What benefits did the Ashina Tribe give you?

221
00:14:03,279 --> 00:14:05,440
Instead of earning merit of punishing the rebels,

222
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:07,360
you'd rather serve as Yan Li's slave.

223
00:14:08,320 --> 00:14:09,320
Your Highness.

224
00:14:09,879 --> 00:14:10,960
Do you really think...

225
00:14:10,960 --> 00:14:12,480
