235
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:36,559
You'll all be doomed.

236
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:38,720
Your Highness doesn't have to worry about that.

237
00:14:39,399 --> 00:14:41,559
You should worry about yourself.

238
00:15:36,600 --> 00:15:37,600
Hao Du.

239
00:15:38,519 --> 00:15:40,159
Don't disappoint me.

240
00:16:03,240 --> 00:16:04,960
Why is Shu Yu...

241
00:16:07,399 --> 00:16:08,480
Chang...

242
00:16:08,759 --> 00:16:09,759
Don't shout.

243
00:16:10,919 --> 00:16:12,440
If you call her, she's dead.

244
00:16:13,879 --> 00:16:14,919
Look at that guy.

245
00:16:17,480 --> 00:16:18,919
Li Chang Ge is being watched.

246
00:16:24,440 --> 00:16:25,720
Who are they?

247
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:26,879
I don't know.

248
00:16:27,639 --> 00:16:28,960
But since Li Chang Ge is here,

249
00:16:30,039 --> 00:16:31,360
something bad must have happened to Wei Shu Yu.

250
00:16:32,039 --> 00:16:33,279
Shu Yu.

251
00:16:34,200 --> 00:16:35,919
If you don't want anything to happen to Wei Shu Yu,

252
00:16:36,679 --> 00:16:37,960
stay here.

253
00:16:38,080 --> 00:16:39,080
Stay still.

254
00:17:00,240 --> 00:17:01,240
