258
00:18:11,170 --> 00:18:12,200
Who are you?

259
00:18:12,599 --> 00:18:14,170
I advise you to hand the item over.

260
00:18:14,519 --> 00:18:17,079
Or else, I'll behead your master.

261
00:18:18,319 --> 00:18:19,359
Go ahead.

262
00:18:20,480 --> 00:18:21,480
