264
00:18:25,200 --> 00:18:26,720
I need to take it back to report the completion of my task.

265
00:18:28,359 --> 00:18:29,519
You're not one of her people.

266
00:18:31,039 --> 00:18:32,240
Who exactly are you?

267
00:18:33,650 --> 00:18:37,000
