268
00:19:01,079 --> 00:19:02,240
Wei Shu Yu is in trouble.

269
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:04,000
I figured.

270
00:19:04,799 --> 00:19:05,839
Hao Du.

271
00:19:13,440 --> 00:19:14,480
Chang Ge?

272
00:19:22,599 --> 00:19:23,599
Chang Ge.

273
00:19:23,759 --> 00:19:24,799
Let her go.

274
00:19:25,039 --> 00:19:26,119
You first.

275
00:19:27,799 --> 00:19:28,799
A life for a life.

276
00:19:29,240 --> 00:19:30,240
That's fair.

277
00:19:33,119 --> 00:19:34,119
Le Yan.

278
00:19:34,920 --> 00:19:35,920
Why are you here?

279
00:19:36,240 --> 00:19:37,650
Chang Ge, I...

280
00:19:38,170 --> 00:19:39,240
What are you waiting for?

281
00:19:40,410 --> 00:19:42,480
The one in my hands is a Tang princess.

282
00:19:42,680 --> 00:19:44,519
Then do you know who I have in my hands?

283
00:19:46,200 --> 00:19:47,440
I don't care who she is.

284
00:19:48,319 --> 00:19:49,319
Let her go.

285
00:19:53,799 --> 00:19:54,799
I'll count to three.

286
00:19:55,359 --> 00:19:56,359
If you don't let her go,

287
00:19:56,890 --> 00:19:58,519
this woman is dead.

288
00:19:58,519 --> 00:19:59,519
Qin Zhun.

289
00:19:59,759 --> 00:20:00,799
Don't do anything reckless.

290
00:20:02,650 --> 00:20:03,650
Hao Du.

291
00:20:04,039 --> 00:20:05,519
Don't hurt Chang Ge.

292
00:20:05,680 --> 00:20:06,680
Let her go.

293
00:20:07,039 --> 00:20:08,039
Hao Du.

294
00:20:10,720 --> 00:20:11,720
One.

295
00:20:17,920 --> 00:20:19,319
If we don't leave now, Wang Jun Kuo will bring his men.

296
00:20:19,319 --> 00:20:20,319
None of us will be able to leave then.

297
00:20:20,440 --> 00:20:21,440
Two.

298
00:20:24,440 --> 00:20:25,480
Who are you?

299
00:20:29,759 --> 00:20:30,759
Three.

300
00:21:33,599 --> 00:21:34,680
- Chang Ge.
- Let's go.

301
00:21:34,680 --> 00:21:35,759
Chang Ge, hurry and go.

302
00:21:35,759 --> 00:21:37,170
- Chang Ge!
- Your Highness.

303
00:21:38,359 --> 00:21:39,359
Your Highness.

304
00:21:41,039 --> 00:21:42,410
- Chang Ge, hurry and leave!
- I'm sorry, Your Highness.

305
00:22:05,519 --> 00:22:06,880
Didn't you already leave long ago?

306
00:22:08,480 --> 00:22:09,480
I...

307
00:22:11,680 --> 00:22:12,720
I came back to take care of something.

308
00:22:12,920 --> 00:22:14,000
Take care of something?

309
00:22:15,119 --> 00:22:17,559
Do you want your horse back from Wang Jun Kuo...

310
00:22:18,039 --> 00:22:19,480
or are you helping Wang Jun Kuo collude with the Ashina Tribe...

311
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:20,680
as their middleman?

312
00:22:22,000 --> 00:22:23,000
Qin Zhun.

313
00:22:23,839 --> 00:22:25,240
Don't force me to become your enemy.

314
00:22:29,400 --> 00:22:30,599
I was just trying to save you.

315
00:22:36,640 --> 00:22:37,640
Thank you for saving me.

316
00:22:38,839 --> 00:22:40,200
I won't ask about the past anymore.

317
00:22:40,880 --> 00:22:42,039
But from now on,

318
00:22:42,640 --> 00:22:45,039
stay out of my business and leave Youzhou.

319
00:22:45,240 --> 00:22:47,039
I think I should be the one to say that.

320
00:22:48,200 --> 00:22:49,640
Those people won't let you off.

321
00:22:49,880 --> 00:22:51,359
If you go back now, you're going to die.

322
00:22:51,640 --> 00:22:52,640
Come with me.

323
00:22:54,519 --> 00:22:56,039
I don't need you to tell me what to do.

324
00:22:56,799 --> 00:22:59,559
I definitely won't let Youzhou fall into the Ashina Tribe's hands.

325
00:23:00,279 --> 00:23:01,440
If you keep following me,

326
00:23:01,759 --> 00:23:02,759
I'll report you.

327
00:23:03,079 --> 00:23:04,319
The imperial court is trying to kill you.

328
00:23:04,319 --> 00:23:05,759
Why are you still working for them?

329
00:23:05,759 --> 00:23:07,759
I just hate the people who destroyed my family.

330
00:23:08,319 --> 00:23:09,759
But I'm still a citizen of Tang.

331
00:23:21,480 --> 00:23:22,480
Didn't you always want it?

332
00:23:23,200 --> 00:23:24,200
Take it for self-defense.

333
00:23:45,400 --> 00:23:47,160
Let go. You're hurting me.

334
00:23:50,119 --> 00:23:51,279
Hao Du, let go of me.

335
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:52,480
Let go.

336
00:23:57,039 --> 00:23:59,400
Didn't you hear Chang Ge say...

337
00:23:59,680 --> 00:24:01,319
that Shu Yu is in trouble just now?

338
00:24:01,799 --> 00:24:03,519
I only care about where Li Chang Ge is.

339
00:24:03,640 --> 00:24:04,640
But...

340
00:24:04,960 --> 00:24:06,799
- Shu Yu...
- I'll say it again.

341
00:24:07,759 --> 00:24:09,200
I only care about Li Chang Ge.

342
00:24:11,200 --> 00:24:12,200
I'm here.

343
00:24:14,400 --> 00:24:15,400
Chang Ge.

344
00:24:16,160 --> 00:24:17,160
Chang Ge.

345
00:24:17,359 --> 00:24:18,599
Chang Ge, why did you come back?

346
00:24:18,599 --> 00:24:20,519
If you move again, I'll kill her right now.

347
00:24:24,839 --> 00:24:25,839
Li Chang Ge.

348
00:24:26,319 --> 00:24:27,319
Are you not running anymore?

349
00:24:27,440 --> 00:24:28,559
If you don't listen to me,

350
00:24:29,079 --> 00:24:30,240
none of us are going anywhere.

351
00:24:32,119 --> 00:24:33,119
Listen to you?

352
00:24:33,759 --> 00:24:35,440
Do you still think you're a princess?

353
00:24:35,599 --> 00:24:36,759
Li Yuan and Wang Jun Kuo...

354
00:24:36,759 --> 00:24:38,400
colluded with the Ashina Tribe's Young Khan.

355
00:24:38,640 --> 00:24:40,359
They're planning to give Youzhou to the Ashina Tribe.

356
00:24:40,880 --> 00:24:43,039
A vicious army is currently coming to Youzhou.

357
00:24:44,240 --> 00:24:45,519
Do you think we can still run?

358
00:24:47,079 --> 00:24:48,079
Don't doubt it.

359
00:24:48,359 --> 00:24:49,440
Wei Shu Yu...

360
00:24:49,440 --> 00:24:51,119
is locked up in the dungeon of the governor's manor now.

361
00:24:51,319 --> 00:24:52,880
If it weren't for the sake of Youzhou,

362
00:24:53,119 --> 00:24:54,720
I wouldn't be standing in front of you right now.

363
00:24:55,640 --> 00:24:56,640
Hao Du.

364
00:24:56,759 --> 00:24:57,960
Let's go and save Shu Yu...

365
00:24:57,960 --> 00:24:58,960
Why should I trust you?

366
00:25:00,400 --> 00:25:02,160
Based on the fact that I'm the one standing here now,

367
00:25:02,160 --> 00:25:03,160
not Wei Shu Yu.

368
00:25:03,279 --> 00:25:04,920
Wei Shu Yu has the entire Wei family behind him.

369
00:25:05,440 --> 00:25:07,319
Do you think he would risk his whole family's life...

370
00:25:07,480 --> 00:25:08,680
to put on an act with me?

371
00:25:17,160 --> 00:25:18,160
There's no need to look around.

372
00:25:18,160 --> 00:25:19,160
I'm alone.

373
00:25:20,160 --> 00:25:21,319
Why are you unscathed?

374
00:25:21,599 --> 00:25:23,160
Because the Crown Prince's seal is in my hands.

375
00:25:23,559 --> 00:25:24,599
Hand it over.

376
00:25:25,599 --> 00:25:26,880
Youzhou is about to fall into the enemy's hands,

377
00:25:27,039 --> 00:25:28,400
yet you're still concerned about that?

378
00:25:28,400 --> 00:25:29,920
Youzhou has nothing to do with me.

379
00:25:30,640 --> 00:25:31,759
My priority...

380
00:25:31,920 --> 00:25:34,200
is to bring you and the Crown Prince's seal back.

381
00:25:34,480 --> 00:25:35,599
Nothing to do with you?

382
00:25:36,240 --> 00:25:37,759
How could a general of the court say that the fall of Youzhou...

383
00:25:37,759 --> 00:25:38,920
has nothing to do with him?

384
00:25:39,839 --> 00:25:40,880
If Du Ru Hui were to hear...

385
00:25:40,880 --> 00:25:42,000
how you have no regard for the bigger picture,

386
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:43,039
he'd kill you.

387
00:25:43,200 --> 00:25:44,359
Don't talk about my godfather.

388
00:25:45,480 --> 00:25:46,920
Why is a thief who stole the Crown Prince's seal...

389
00:25:46,920 --> 00:25:48,200
talking to me about the bigger picture?

390
00:25:51,559 --> 00:25:52,559
Li Chang Ge.

391
00:25:53,720 --> 00:25:55,119
Even if what you said is true,

392
00:25:55,680 --> 00:25:56,920
I won't let you run away again.

393
00:25:57,119 --> 00:25:58,200
You're ignoring urgent priorities.

394
00:25:58,200 --> 00:25:59,440
You only care about your personal gain.

395
00:25:59,640 --> 00:26:01,079
How will you accomplish great things with such a mindset?

396
00:26:01,079 --> 00:26:02,839
Regardless of what I accomplish, I don't need you to teach me.

397
00:26:03,200 --> 00:26:05,400
Bringing back the Crown Prince's seal is the most important thing.

398
00:26:05,559 --> 00:26:06,839
If Wang Jun Kuo gets his way,

399
00:26:07,160 --> 00:26:09,480
it'll be too late even if we ask the court to send an army in.

400
00:26:17,920 --> 00:26:18,920
Li Chang Ge.

401
00:26:19,599 --> 00:26:21,279
I don't care whether this is all true or not.

402
00:26:22,039 --> 00:26:23,480
My priority right now...

403
00:26:23,480 --> 00:26:25,319
is to safely get the princess out of Youzhou.

404
00:26:25,839 --> 00:26:27,720
If you still think of the princess as your friend,

405
00:26:27,920 --> 00:26:28,920
then cooperate.

406
00:26:35,680 --> 00:26:36,680
Useless!

407
00:26:36,680 --> 00:26:37,680
There are so many of you,

408
00:26:37,880 --> 00:26:39,160
yet you lost her.

409
00:26:39,799 --> 00:26:40,839
I'm sorry.

410
00:26:40,960 --> 00:26:43,039
I've ordered people to search the city for Li Chang Ge.

411
00:26:43,519 --> 00:26:44,880
I've also given orders to close off the city gates.

412
00:26:45,079 --> 00:26:46,559
I don't care what method you use.

413
00:26:47,039 --> 00:26:48,559
I must get it by tomorrow.

414
00:26:48,680 --> 00:26:49,759
Otherwise, when we face Young Khan,

415
00:26:49,880 --> 00:26:51,279
you and I will be in big trouble.

416
00:26:51,400 --> 00:26:52,400
Governor.

417
00:26:52,960 --> 00:26:54,079
I have something else to report.

418
00:26:54,599 --> 00:26:57,359
I've discovered that there's another group...

419
00:26:57,799 --> 00:26:59,319
tracking down Li Chang Ge as well.

420
00:27:00,039 --> 00:27:01,799
That man is skilled in martial arts. He's even better than me.

421
00:27:01,799 --> 00:27:03,039
He's definitely not a martial artist.

422
00:27:03,720 --> 00:27:04,880
Could he be from the imperial court?

423
00:27:05,759 --> 00:27:06,799
Then our plans...

424
00:27:06,799 --> 00:27:08,519
Governor, you don't have to worry.

425
00:27:09,599 --> 00:27:10,720
That person doesn't care...

426
00:27:10,720 --> 00:27:12,200
whether Li Chang Ge is dead or alive at all.

427
00:27:12,640 --> 00:27:14,039
He just wants to capture her.

428
00:27:14,640 --> 00:27:16,440
So I suspect that person...

429
00:27:16,440 --> 00:27:18,400
may also be after the Crown Prince's seal.

430
00:27:27,079 --> 00:27:28,200
At this point,

431
00:27:30,160 --> 00:27:31,680
there's no turning back.

432
00:27:32,079 --> 00:27:33,799
I want both Li Chang Ge and the people...

433
00:27:33,960 --> 00:27:35,359
- from the imperial court.
- I got it.

434
00:27:36,400 --> 00:27:37,640
As long as she's alive,

435
00:27:38,119 --> 00:27:40,039
she won't be able to leave Youzhou City.

436
00:27:42,440 --> 00:27:44,680
Has Young Khan made any moves?

437
00:27:45,880 --> 00:27:47,920
Yan Li Khan's army is heading south soon.

438
00:27:48,440 --> 00:27:50,039
All we have to do is prevent any news of Youzhou City...

439
00:27:50,039 --> 00:27:51,400
or other places from getting out.

440
00:27:51,559 --> 00:27:53,599
Once Young Khan's big army arrives,

441
00:27:54,440 --> 00:27:55,920
we won't have to worry about anything.

442
00:27:56,480 --> 00:27:58,160
Both our glory...

443
00:27:59,039 --> 00:28:00,480
depends on this.

444
00:28:01,279 --> 00:28:02,680
Yes, Governor.

445
00:28:22,039 --> 00:28:23,200
Hurry! Close the gate!

446
00:28:23,200 --> 00:28:24,319
No one may enter or leave.

447
00:28:24,319 --> 00:28:26,319
Close the gate? Why the rush?

448
00:28:26,440 --> 00:28:28,200
This is General Wang's order. Hurry and follow through.

449
00:28:28,440 --> 00:28:30,200
If the criminal escapes, it's on you.

450
00:28:30,200 --> 00:28:31,200
Yes.

451
00:28:33,759 --> 00:28:38,920
(Youzhou)

452
00:28:54,279 --> 00:28:55,279
Chang Ge.

453
00:28:56,319 --> 00:28:57,519
I've always liked to lean on your shoulder...

454
00:28:57,519 --> 00:28:58,839
ever since we were young.

455
00:28:59,480 --> 00:29:03,720
I feel reassured whenever you're around.

456
00:29:07,359 --> 00:29:08,519
I don't care if you're anxious.

457
00:29:09,400 --> 00:29:10,640
I don't know...

458
00:29:11,720 --> 00:29:13,839
how long it'll be until the next time...

459
00:29:15,000 --> 00:29:16,720
I can lean on your shoulder.

460
00:29:21,799 --> 00:29:22,920
Untie me.

461
00:29:23,119 --> 00:29:24,119
My hands hurt.

462
00:29:32,400 --> 00:29:33,400
Li Chang Ge.

463
00:29:33,759 --> 00:29:34,880
You're underestimating me.

464
00:29:44,480 --> 00:29:46,759
(Rest stop)

465
00:30:19,640 --> 00:30:21,359
Is capturing Chang Ge really that important?

466
00:30:24,720 --> 00:30:25,960
Is it more important than our lives,

467
00:30:25,960 --> 00:30:27,200
the entire Youzhou City,

468
00:30:27,200 --> 00:30:28,880
and the lives of the civilians?

469
00:30:29,640 --> 00:30:30,960
Youzhou has been sealed off.

470
00:30:31,559 --> 00:30:32,960
I can't save the people of Youzhou.

471
00:30:34,200 --> 00:30:35,359
I can't save Wei Shu Yu either.

472
00:30:36,519 --> 00:30:39,359
So you're just going to watch Shu Yu die?

473
00:30:41,039 --> 00:30:42,160
We'll send a smoke signal outside the city...

474
00:30:42,279 --> 00:30:43,319
and inform the court.

475
00:30:43,799 --> 00:30:44,960
This is the only way.

476
00:30:48,880 --> 00:30:49,920
You mean...

477
00:30:50,960 --> 00:30:52,400
Shu Yu can be saved?

478
00:30:53,000 --> 00:30:54,079
We can only leave it up to fate.

479
00:31:25,160 --> 00:31:26,160
It's you?

480
00:31:26,440 --> 00:31:27,440
Hurry in.

481
00:31:29,920 --> 00:31:30,920
Why are you here?

482
00:31:31,039 --> 00:31:32,759
The peddler told me to wait for you at the city gate.

483
00:31:32,920 --> 00:31:33,960
I stayed there the whole time.

484
00:31:34,119 --> 00:31:35,119
I didn't even blink.

485
00:31:35,680 --> 00:31:36,680
Then,

486
00:31:36,960 --> 00:31:38,759
I saw soldiers sealing the gates.

487
00:31:39,039 --> 00:31:41,039
Only one carriage left the city at the last minute.

488
00:31:41,599 --> 00:31:43,200
I guessed that would probably be the last chance...

489
00:31:43,200 --> 00:31:44,400
for you to escape.

490
00:31:44,559 --> 00:31:45,559
So I followed the carriage.

491
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:49,680
That peddler was indeed right.

492
00:31:50,559 --> 00:31:51,559
What did he say?

493
00:31:51,759 --> 00:31:53,519
He said he believes that you'll definitely escape.

494
00:31:55,480 --> 00:31:56,839
- Where is it?
- It's here.

495
00:31:58,240 --> 00:31:59,359
It's here with me.

496
00:32:02,759 --> 00:32:03,799
By the way, Master,

497
00:32:04,319 --> 00:32:05,519
who kidnapped you?

498
00:32:06,119 --> 00:32:07,119
They're from Chang'an.

499
00:32:07,400 --> 00:32:08,759
They've even made it all the way to Youzhou?

500
00:32:09,480 --> 00:32:10,960
The situation is very urgent now.

501
00:32:11,200 --> 00:32:12,680
I'm going to need reinforcements.

502
00:32:12,960 --> 00:32:14,559
Dou, wait for me here.

503
00:32:14,559 --> 00:32:15,559
Master.

504
00:32:16,119 --> 00:32:17,319
Don't leave me again.

505
00:32:18,039 --> 00:32:20,160
What I'm facing now is a major army from Youzhou.

506
00:32:20,440 --> 00:32:21,559
If I don't go over there now...

507
00:32:21,680 --> 00:32:22,720
and Wang Jun Kuo gets his way,

508
00:32:22,880 --> 00:32:24,240
there really won't be any way to escape then.

509
00:32:24,440 --> 00:32:25,839
Then why are you still going?

510
00:32:25,960 --> 00:32:27,200
Because I don't have any choice.

511
00:32:27,759 --> 00:32:28,759
Besides,

512
00:32:29,319 --> 00:32:30,519
I don't believe the Youzhou army...

513
00:32:30,519 --> 00:32:31,960
will become stooges like Wang Jun Kuo.

514
00:32:32,319 --> 00:32:33,319
Master.

515
00:32:33,839 --> 00:32:34,920
Don't leave me again.

516
00:32:35,039 --> 00:32:36,599
Fighting on the battlefield is my dream.

517
00:32:36,599 --> 00:32:37,880
I want to see a real army.

518
00:32:37,880 --> 00:32:40,079
I won't let you go on your own no matter what you say this time.

519
00:32:43,720 --> 00:32:44,720
All right.

520
00:32:44,839 --> 00:32:45,839
I'll take you.

521
00:32:45,960 --> 00:32:47,000
I'll let you see...

522
00:32:47,000 --> 00:32:48,319
what a real army looks like.

523
00:32:49,119 --> 00:32:50,160
All right.

524
00:32:50,359 --> 00:32:52,359
Before I go, I need to meet someone.

525
00:32:52,480 --> 00:32:53,480
Wait for me outside.

526
00:33:08,000 --> 00:33:09,000
Chang Ge.

527
00:33:11,599 --> 00:33:12,960
Tell Hao Du to take you back to Chang'an.

528
00:33:12,960 --> 00:33:14,079
It's not safe to stay here.

529
00:33:15,000 --> 00:33:16,000
Chang Ge.

530
00:33:16,920 --> 00:33:18,400
I can't go back to Chang'an.

531
00:33:19,759 --> 00:33:21,519
Grandfather wants to marry me off to the prairies...

532
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:23,720
and intermarry with the Ashina Tribe.

533
00:33:23,720 --> 00:33:24,720
What?

534
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:28,119
But my father said I'm very sick...

535
00:33:28,119 --> 00:33:29,720
and told me to recuperate in Luoyang.

536
00:33:31,680 --> 00:33:32,720
Listen to your father.

537
00:33:33,119 --> 00:33:34,200
Be good and stay in Luoyang.

538
00:33:37,240 --> 00:33:38,240
Chang Ge.

539
00:33:39,640 --> 00:33:41,359
But I don't want to go anywhere.

540
00:33:42,839 --> 00:33:44,759
I really want things to go back to the way they were.

541
00:34:05,440 --> 00:34:06,440
That can't happen.

542
00:34:08,559 --> 00:34:09,559
Then...

543
00:34:10,920 --> 00:34:13,360
Then can we still see each other again?

544
00:34:18,559 --> 00:34:19,599
It's best that we don't.

545
00:34:20,440 --> 00:34:21,440
Chang Ge.

546
00:34:23,639 --> 00:34:24,769
Hao Du said that...

547
00:34:24,769 --> 00:34:26,719
sending a smoke signal is our only chance.

548
00:34:29,289 --> 00:34:31,239
Do you think Shu Yu can be saved?

549
00:34:32,199 --> 00:34:33,519
I'll definitely save him.

550
00:34:34,079 --> 00:34:35,079
Don't worry.

551
00:35:06,079 --> 00:35:09,079
Youngsters these days are always in such a scurry.

552
00:35:11,960 --> 00:35:13,769
By the way, Youzhou has been sealed off.

553
00:35:14,480 --> 00:35:16,599
They have given orders not to let anyone in or out.

554
00:35:17,480 --> 00:35:18,719
It's getting late.

555
00:35:18,920 --> 00:35:19,920
There's a rest stop up ahead.

556
00:35:20,400 --> 00:35:21,880
We can take a break there.

557
00:35:22,159 --> 00:35:24,039
Just go with the flow.

558
00:35:24,480 --> 00:35:27,440
Life is full of surprises.

559
00:35:29,329 --> 00:35:30,400
Isn't that right?

560
00:35:31,199 --> 00:35:32,400
Su Su.

561
00:35:35,960 --> 00:35:36,960
Let's go.

562
00:35:49,920 --> 00:35:50,920
Stop right there.

563
00:35:51,400 --> 00:35:52,400
What are you doing?

564
00:35:52,639 --> 00:35:53,639
Here's my seal.

565
00:35:53,769 --> 00:35:55,400
