566
00:35:56,480 --> 00:35:57,480
Let him in.

567
00:36:07,159 --> 00:36:09,360
(Share weal and woe)

568
00:36:13,639 --> 00:36:15,079
You're saying Governor Li and General Wang...

569
00:36:15,079 --> 00:36:16,159
have defected to the enemy?

570
00:36:16,639 --> 00:36:17,639
What proof do you have?

571
00:36:17,880 --> 00:36:19,519
The envoys and subordinates that came with me...

572
00:36:19,719 --> 00:36:21,329
are all locked up in the dungeon of the governor's manor.

573
00:36:21,480 --> 00:36:23,289
If you and your soldiers come along with me,

574
00:36:23,289 --> 00:36:25,079
you'll see for yourself.

575
00:36:25,769 --> 00:36:26,809
Soldiers from outside the city...

576
00:36:26,809 --> 00:36:28,199
are not allowed to enter without a military order.

577
00:36:28,880 --> 00:36:30,440
If you don't have any other evidence,

578
00:36:30,809 --> 00:36:32,769
