579
00:36:33,039 --> 00:36:34,840
But the city is being controlled by Wang Jun Kuo's followers.

580
00:36:35,039 --> 00:36:36,519
As soon as the Ashina Tribe's army arrives,

581
00:36:36,840 --> 00:36:39,289
Li Yuan will hand Youzhou over to them.

582
00:36:39,480 --> 00:36:41,400
The north of Tang will be defenseless.

583
00:36:42,519 --> 00:36:44,039
Everything I'm saying is true.

584
00:36:44,519 --> 00:36:45,769
Please dispatch your troops.

585
00:36:47,719 --> 00:36:49,880
What if I refuse?

586
00:36:54,079 --> 00:36:55,079
Then...

587
00:36:55,960 --> 00:36:57,159
