588
00:36:58,639 --> 00:36:59,840
You're not an envoy from Chang'an.

589
00:36:59,840 --> 00:37:00,920
Speak.

590
00:37:00,920 --> 00:37:02,079
Who are you?

591
00:37:06,119 --> 00:37:07,119
Captain.

592
00:37:08,840 --> 00:37:09,840
Captain.

593
00:37:09,840 --> 00:37:10,960
There's a smoke signal.

594
00:37:11,199 --> 00:37:12,199
Smoke signal?

595
00:37:23,440 --> 00:37:24,519
It's a smoke signal.

596
00:37:26,159 --> 00:37:27,769
Captain, please send out your troops immediately.

597
00:37:28,159 --> 00:37:29,159
Convey my orders.

598
00:37:29,360 --> 00:37:30,880
- Assemble the entire army.
- Yes.

599
00:38:21,400 --> 00:38:22,400
Your Highness.

600
00:38:22,400 --> 00:38:23,400
How is it?

601
00:38:24,039 --> 00:38:25,079
The word got out.

602
00:38:25,079 --> 00:38:26,079
The Tang soldiers are on alert now.

603
00:38:26,559 --> 00:38:27,639
We have to leave now.

604
00:38:29,679 --> 00:38:30,920
Wang Jun Kuo, that piece of trash.

605
00:38:34,119 --> 00:38:35,360
