609
00:38:42,039 --> 00:38:43,679
The carriage is hiding in the woods outside the city.

610
00:38:43,809 --> 00:38:44,809
Good.

611
00:38:45,360 --> 00:38:46,440
We didn't come here for nothing.

612
00:38:47,289 --> 00:38:49,289
Let's leave the city with Wang Jun Kuo's command token.

613
00:38:50,000 --> 00:38:51,000
Yes.

614
00:39:07,159 --> 00:39:08,199
Stop.

615
00:39:13,679 --> 00:39:15,289
