619
00:39:58,400 --> 00:40:00,119
If you expose yourself now, it'll be hard to escape.

620
00:40:01,119 --> 00:40:02,960
Your Highness, you're someone of special status.

621
00:40:03,079 --> 00:40:04,400
We can't let anything go wrong.

622
00:40:04,679 --> 00:40:05,679
Let's go.

623
00:40:06,000 --> 00:40:07,000
Come on.

624
00:40:07,920 --> 00:40:08,920
Come on.

625
00:40:16,239 --> 00:40:17,639
It seems like someone is hiding over there.

626
00:40:18,480 --> 00:40:19,719
- Go and take a look.
- Yes.

627
00:40:41,199 --> 00:40:42,880
This is from the Youzhou vault.

628
00:40:44,920 --> 00:40:46,239
It seems like there must be trouble in the city.

629
00:40:46,639 --> 00:40:48,079
Convey my orders. We must speed up.

630
00:40:48,519 --> 00:40:50,599
We must get to Youzhou City before dawn.

631
00:40:51,119 --> 00:40:52,199
- Yes.
- Yes.

632
00:40:53,880 --> 00:40:57,000
